You can see the [[en/Recent and Current Developments|latest developments]], [[en/roadmap|expected features for the upcoming releases]] and the [[en/requested features]] list if you're interested in the current state of the project. If you're already a developer, the [[en/Development Documentation]] is useful.

We also have a development community on our [[en/Development/IRC channel]] and in the [http://www.tt-forums.net/viewforum.php?f=33 development forum].
